{"tid":2159521,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"今晚 2100 直播 頭條動新聞ep.3 20200816","createTime":"2020-08-16T11:14:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T12:53:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d434ffef5e3d76698bdf71d77467cb8da1933085","tid":2159521,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T11:14:33.000Z","msg":"#Appledaily #StayHome #WithMe<br />\n<br />\n2100 直播<br />\n頭條動新聞ep.3 (蘋果日報 Appledaily)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PVguV-uXMQc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPVguV-uXMQc&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJBD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=ad3ec5f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PVguV-uXMQc</a><br />\n<br />\n蘋果動新聞 HK Apple Daily<br />\n1.7M subscribers<br />\n<br />\n面對強權打壓，批判政府的聲音越來越少，《頭條動新聞》請來《四點鐘王Sir》主持王喜，以及《AppleDaily Show豪》主持曾志豪，繼續與香港人一同嬉笑怒罵、諷刺時弊。<br />\n<br />\n《四點鐘王Sir》<br />\n大台藝人Easy Sir楊明今次終於可以於現實世界和警隊連成一線，日前於山頂撞車腳步浮浮，其後聲稱不適的他最終並非由救護員送上白車，而是由數名軍裝警帶上警車送到醫院，警員為何有此特權搶去救護員工作？加上楊明撐警撐出面，為警察願意付出一切代價，究竟是甚麼代價？<br />\n<br />\n《AppleDaily Show豪》<br />\n國安法下搜報館，Show豪以為節目就此取消，幸好見到最資深員工黎智英繼續精神上班，加上讀者支持，故決定繼續開騷。<br />\n<br />\n撐同路人計劃 自由定價支持<br />\n如果你想支持《頭條動新聞》的兩位創作人曾志豪和王喜，可以透過「撐同路人計劃」，以自由定價力撐他們。我們誠邀你在YouTube收看本節目直播期間（暫時只限YouTube平台及本節目的直播時段內），按留言位右邊的按鈕。你可以選擇購買得意可愛的「Super Sticker」，或以自由定價的「超級即時通訊」作支持。你的一分一毫在扣除成本後，會全數撥歸此節目的合作夥伴，《蘋果》與你攜手撐同路人！<br />\n<br />\n蘋果日報 ： <a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJBD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=abf2454e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com&h=bbd68420\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com</a><br />\n即 like 蘋果 fb  ： <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJBD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=e0fcd2c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia</a><br />\niPhone App ： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/AppleDailyApp-iPhone\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FAppleDailyApp-iPhone&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJBD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=3361d586\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/AppleDailyApp-iPhone</a><br />\nAndroid App ： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/AppleDailyApp-Android\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FAppleDailyApp-Android&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJBD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=cd12dc4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/AppleDailyApp-Android</a>"},{"pid":"07026a964ffc9c5ab0529ae79284a21a1ab19e6b","tid":2159521,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T12:18:49.000Z","msg":"42 mins"},{"pid":"ba9858b3b7d9dc977ce62225263f58ec5f45119a","tid":2159521,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T12:30:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a4bd58b0d7a6eb448d8b2fed681383eb1043896","tid":2159521,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T12:46:40.000Z","msg":"13 mins"},{"pid":"5585e01c5865b3a6e01cab917158ba900ecf3b94","tid":2159521,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T12:56:32.000Z","msg":"3 mins"},{"pid":"ba82fa435912079ae5dec10a2d389ed0d54d5dc1","tid":2159521,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T12:59:53.000Z","msg":"1 min"},{"pid":"3f1ac56a4d533dbecd9d3cbff6eefee6a4ceabbd","tid":2159521,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T13:02:54.000Z","msg":"開波"},{"pid":"d8521e6f47f9308e81291957a872ece701bdac2c","tid":2159521,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T13:03:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"